<p>About 7 months ago, I seriously started to focus in ML field. And right now, I have done many considerable good things. I have done projects like “<a href="https://github.com/prashant-kikani/toxic-comment-classifier">toxic-comment-classifier</a>”, “<a href="https://github.com/prashant-kikani/sarcasm-detector-by-CNN">sarcasm-detector</a>”, “<a href="https://github.com/prashant-kikani/movie-recommender">movie-recommender</a>” etc. And some “non-ML” projects like <a href="https://github.com/prashant-kikani/image-optimizer">image-optimizer</a> and an online gaming site to play Tic-Tac-Toe against unbeatable bot. Also I am an “<a href="https://www.kaggle.com/prashantkikani">expert</a>” in Kaggle kernels and doing summer Internship in Deep learning in Bangalore, India.</p>

